Sentencas: Too high stack temperature and insufficient reactant gas flow may lead to severe and irreversible damages in a real solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) power system.
Titulo: Fault Diagnosis of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Based on a Supervised Self-Organization Map Model

Sentencas: Thus, fault monitoring and diagnosis technology is indispensable to improve the SOFC system reliability.
Titulo: Fault Diagnosis of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Based on a Supervised Self-Organization Map Model

Sentencas: A supervised self-organization map (SOM) model is proposed to diagnose the faults of the SOFC system in this paper.
Titulo: Fault Diagnosis of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Based on a Supervised Self-Organization Map Model

Sentencas: Using the supervised SOM model, the multidimensional testing data of the SOFC is mapped into a two-dimensional map, and the different region in the out map is represented for one fault mode.
Titulo: Fault Diagnosis of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Based on a Supervised Self-Organization Map Model

Sentencas: The method is evaluated using the data obtained from an SOFC mathematical model, and the results show that the supervised SOM analysis contributes on a very efficient way to the faults diagnosis of the SOFC system.
Titulo: Fault Diagnosis of Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Based on a Supervised Self-Organization Map Model
